# honggfuzz build artifacts (instrumented binaries + libhfuzz.a)
hfuzz_target/

# honggfuzz campaign workspace (corpus, crash reproducers, stats).
# Crash reproducers SHOULD be committed under a curated regression
# directory once triaged; the raw workspace is too noisy to track.
hfuzz_workspace/

# Cargo build artifacts (this dir is a standalone workspace, so cargo
# drops a target/ here as well).
target/

# NOTE: Cargo.lock IS committed (not ignored). The fuzz crate is a
# binary workspace, and reproducible fuzz runs require lockfile
# pinning of honggfuzz, arbitrary, and the agent-registry path dep
# transitive graph. Same convention as `programs/*/Cargo.lock` (root
# `Cargo.lock` is the source of truth for those).
